### Get all vehicles
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles

###

### Get vehicle by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/1

###

### Create vehicle
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "Mazda",
  "model": "CX-5",
  "year": 2020,
  "licensePlate": "MAZ2020",
  "dailyRate": 75.00,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Update vehicle
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "make": "Toyota",
  "model": "Corolla SE",
  "year": 2022,
  "licensePlate": "ABC1234",
  "dailyRate": 65.00,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

###

### Delete vehicle
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/5